{"questionId":"19197","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Points in the plane are subjected to a transformation <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>T</mi></math> in which the point <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>)</mo></math> is transformed to the point <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mi>y</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>)</mo></math>&nbsp;where</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi><mo>'</mo></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi><mo>'</mo></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mtable><mtr><mtd><mn>3</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mn>0</mn></mtd><mtd><mn>2</mn></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced><mfenced open=\"[\" close=\"]\"><mtable><mtr><mtd><mi>x</mi></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mi>y</mi></mtd></mtr></mtable></mfenced></math>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find the coordinates of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>A',&nbsp;B',&nbsp;C',&nbsp;D'</mtext></math>, the points to which <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>A,&nbsp;B,&nbsp;C,&nbsp;D</mtext></math> are transformed under <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>T</mi></math>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p>the transformed points are</p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>A'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>8</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>B'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>12</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>16</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>C'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>24</mn><mo>,</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>D'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>15</mn><mo>,</mo><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A2</strong></em></p>\n<p><strong><br>Note:</strong> Award <em><strong>A1</strong></em> if one point is incorrect.</p>\n<p><em><strong><br>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"19197","referenceCode":"20N.1.AHL.TZ0.F_7b.iii","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Find the coordinates of A', B', C', D', the points to which A, B, C, D are transformed under T.","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"b.iii","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","AHL 3.9—Matrix transformations"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}